        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 2. Halicyclops continentalis new species, female. (A) Habitus, dorsal; (B) urosome with P5 and caudal rami (lengths of dorsal setae are not properly shown because of oblique angles), dorsal; (C) urosome, ventral; (D) middle caudal setae; (E) antennule, ventral; (F) antenna, posterior; (G) mandible, anterior. A–C, E–G, holotype; D, non-type from Kashima-gawa River." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4590583/files/figure.png" .

